19:07.880 --> 19:13.040
Just another day
Planning to get you back

19:14.320 --> 19:18.840
The house is like hell
The memories are burning

19:18.920 --> 19:22.080
And I like a masochist
I left everything as it was

19:22.160 --> 19:24.760
