29:07.120 --> 29:10.240
Black, with oatmeal, matcha tea.

29:13.000 --> 29:14.680
Coffee, coffee.

29:17.560 --> 29:18.560
You can go in now.

29:22.160 --> 29:23.160
Go in.

29:27.520 --> 29:30.200
-I'm fine. There's nothing wrong with me.
-Restart process.

29:30.960 --> 29:33.080
