29:34.040 --> 29:35.360
Restart process.

29:35.440 --> 29:37.240
Real Madrid three, Barça nil.

29:39.160 --> 29:41.520
-You're tickling me.
-Yes, come in, sit down.

29:41.600 --> 29:44.640
-Where are you going? No. Stop.
-I'm perfectly fine.

29:44.720 --> 29:47.280
-Hey, cutie. Stop.
-Someday, we will rule the world.

29:47.360 --> 29:51.440
My secretary has reviewed your résumé,
and your profile is quite interesting.

29:51.520 --> 29:53.520
Do you know what we do?

29:53.600 --> 29:55.040
-Yes, you...
-Stop. Hey, hey.

29:55.120 --> 29:57.360
