29:57.440 --> 30:00.440
You create and position content
in the metaverse.

30:00.520 --> 30:02.120
Stop meowing.

30:03.000 --> 30:03.960
Can I get you a coffee?

30:04.040 --> 30:06.440
-I don't want a coffee now. I don't--
-I'll go get it.

30:06.520 --> 30:08.000
-I think...
-Stop.

30:08.080 --> 30:10.280
I think I could contribute more
in the creative work.

30:10.360 --> 30:13.760
To the other side. Sudo kill. Sudo kill.

30:13.840 --> 30:16.440
-Should I come back at another time?
-No, it's already...

30:16.520 --> 30:19.480
-Stupid humans.
-It's fixed. It was worse before.

30:24.720 --> 30:26.280
We've met, haven't we?

30:28.360 --> 30:30.040
The guy on the flight to Ibiza.

30:30.120 --> 30:31.640
And the one on the motorcycle.

30:34.520 --> 30:38.560
That was you.
