30:38.640 --> 30:39.520
You're great at mime.

30:39.600 --> 30:42.800
I'm telling you this as a professional,
I worked as a mime when I was young.

30:42.880 --> 30:47.200
Yeah. Well, I guess
this is the end of the interview.

30:48.800 --> 30:52.400
By the way, if you still have contacts
in the circus, I could use them.

30:52.480 --> 30:54.760
As you can see,
I was born to be a dumb clown.

30:55.400 --> 30:58.560
I take all the hits. Thank you.

31:12.920 --> 31:14.480
Fuck, it hurts!

